Package: EcoNicheS
Type: Package
Title: An R package for Shiny Ecological Niche Modeling Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2023-05-24
Author: Armando Sunny
Description: An R package for Shiny that enables the analysis of ecological niche modeling using the biomod2 library and other analytics. This is Version 1.0.0, and subsequent versions will be uploaded with additional analyses.
